### new MyClass()->method() without parentheses (Part 6)

- Add a unit test for the navigator

It was observed, that custom @-rules failed to properly parse when there was no whitespace present between the rule and the opening brace.

While this parsed:

```css
    @-ms-viewport {
        width:1024px;
    }
```

This was not:

```css
    @-ms-viewport{
        width:1024px;
    }
```

